|WKBTHE BROOD APOTHECARY
====================

|YKOThe Brood Apothecary is a DarkWind City shop that sells parasite carriers:
larvae, worms, cysts, fleas, and stranger living bargains. These carriers can
be swallowed or eaten to grant elevated hit point regeneration, spell point
regeneration, or both for a finite amount of online time.

The shop is south of Xenor Road. Its stock is level-gated, and some parasites
have additional host requirements.

|WKBSHOP COMMANDS
=============

  |YKBlist parasites|YKO
    Shows available parasite carriers.

  |YKBdescribe parasite <number or name>|YKO
    Shows the required level, regen per pulse, cost, duration, appetite, and
    penalties for a parasite.

  |YKBbuy <number>|YKO
    Buys the numbered parasite carrier from the shop list.

  |YKBpurge parasite|YKO
    Removes your active parasite for a fee.

After buying a carrier, hold it and use |YKBswallow <parasite>|YKO or
|YKBeat <parasite>|YKO to install it. Use |YKBparasite|YKO afterward to inspect
the infection.

See also: |YKBhelp parasites|YKO.
